Takeru\se[1]: "This place is kinda beautiful,
isn't it?"

Boku (So there was such a place in this town
too...)

Takeru\se[2]: "But, we've got to look for the
erotic books!"

Boku\se[3] (So he's really going to search for
that, huh...)

Takeru\se[0]: "Come on, Boku, let's search
together!"

Boku\se[3]: "We searched quite a bit, but no
luck..."

Takeru\se[0]: "Well, can't be helped... But I'm
not giving up!"

Takeru\se[1]: "If there's another place that looks
promising, let's search together again!"

After that, Takeru and I parted ways, and I
returned to town.

Yui\se[0]: "I had no idea a place like this
existed..."

Boku\se[3]: "Well, Yui-chan, you seemed a bit
down. I thought coming to a place like this might
cheer you up a bit..."

Yui\se[2]: "Hehe... Oh, Boku-kun, you're such a
sweetheart... But I'm happy♪"

Yui: "To think they could be seen in this town
too..."

Boku\se[0]: "Yeah, they're glowing and floating
around... It's amazing"

Yui\se[5]: "...You know, I've been thinking about
something"

Yui: "Miyabi-chan and Shoko-chan have dreams for
the future, something to aim for, but I wasn't
quite sure about myself"

Yui: "So, I was feeling a little anxious about
it..."

Yui: "But now, I might have found something I want
to do as well"

Yui\se[1]: "Maybe it's thanks to you, Boku-kun?
Watching these fireflies with you, I suddenly felt
like I found it"

Yui\se[2]: "Yes, thanks to you♪ After all, if you
hadn't brought me here, I wouldn't have seen the
fireflies, right?"

Boku\se[0]: "What kind of dream is it that you've
found, Yui-chan?"

Yui: "Being alone with you makes my heart race...
Shall we do something naughty here?"

Miyabi: "Nfufu♪ No, it's just... walking around
the festival with you gets me so excited, you
know?"

Miyabi: "Should we do something... naughty right
here?"

Miyabi: "It's fine—no one will come by. Besides, I
can't wait any longer...♪"

Shoko: "Well, it might be strange for me to say
this, but..."

Shoko: "Would you like to create some 'memories'
with me here...?"

Shoko: "Ah, yes... I mean, I read on the internet
that boys and girls our age make memories after
slipping away from the summer festival..."

Boku: (I don't quite understand, but maybe she's
suggesting some kind of game...?)
Shoko: "Come on, Boku, come over here...♪"
